Here is my Log file

Hmm, well one thing is for sure, you need to install ModuleManager correctly. What your log shows is that you have a *folder* called ModuleManager - but MM is "special" in that the .DLL file needs to be in GameData, not the folder it came in. So just move the DLL to the GameData folder, and then get rid of the ModuleManager folder entirely.

Maybe just that will clear up some of the other errors in your log - it's definitely something you need, so I would start there and see what happens. There are also a ton of really suspect file names in your KNES install - but I don't know enough about that mod to know if they're fine or not.
